  <Doc.Item>
    <div class="prose prose-lg">
      <p>
        An accessibility helper that allows a component to add an
        <a
          href="https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria-1.1/#attrs_liveregions"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >ARIA live region</a>
        while it is rendered. The component can then handle its own logic for
        what to announce and when;
        <em>this</em>
        component just ensures that there’s an element, “portaled” to the
        top-level of the app, for messages to appear in.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Doc.Item>
